FBIS3-46412 "drchi019_c_94006" FBIS-CHI-94-019 Document Type:Daily Report 29 Jan 1994 Central Eurasia Russian Embassy Holds Reception at Art Exhibition OW2701131594 Beijing XINHUA in English 1236 GMT 27 Jan 94 OW2701131594 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, January 27 (XINHUA) -- The Russian Embassy to China held a reception here this afternoon on the opening of a Russian art exhibition, to welcome Russian Foreign Minister Andrey V. Kozyrev, who is on an official visit to Beijing. Kozyrev and his wife and selected diplomatic envoys in Beijing attended the reception inside the Russian Embassy.
